library(shiny) library(ggplot2) library(plotly) library(dplyr) library(scales) library(shinythemes) load("data_ECI.RData") # Функция для сокращения названий (сокращает до 50 символов в tooltip) shorten_text <- function(text, max_length = 50) { ifelse(nchar(text) > max_length, paste0(substr(text, 1, max_length), "..."), text) } # Функция для нормализации по min/max normalize_minmax <- function(x) { return((x - min(x, na.rm = TRUE)) / (max(x, na.rm = TRUE) - min(x, na.rm = TRUE))) } # UI ui <- fluidPage( theme = shinythemes::shinytheme("flatly"), tags$head( tags$script(HTML(" $(document).on('shiny:connected', function(event) { var width = $(window).width(); var height = $(window).height(); Shiny.setInputValue('client_width', width); Shiny.setInputValue('client_height', height); }); ")), tags$meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"), # **CSS для ограничения размера всплывающих подсказок** tags$style(HTML(" .plotly-tooltip { max-width: 250px !important; /* Ограничиваем ширину */ white-space: normal !important; /* Разрешаем перенос строк */ word-wrap: break-word !important; /* Перенос слов */ } ")) ), h4("ТОП 50 товаров для экспортной диверсификации", style = "text-align: center; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;"), uiOutput("dynamic_ui") ) # Server server <- function(input, output) { is_mobile <- reactive({ req(input$client_width) return(input$client_width < 768) }) output$dynamic_ui <- renderUI({ if (is.null(input$client_width)) { return(NULL) } if (!is_mobile()) { sidebarLayout( sidebarPanel( selectInput("region", "Выберите регион:", choices = colnames(dd), selected = colnames(dd)[1]), radioButtons("policy", "Выберите промышленную политику:", choices = list("Экспансионная" = "expansion", "Сбалансированная" = "balanced", "Сдержанная" = "conservative"), selected = "balanced") ), mainPanel( plotlyOutput("scatterPlot", height = "650px") ) ) } else { fluidRow( column(12, selectInput("region", "Регион:", choices = colnames(dd), selected = colnames(dd)[1]), radioButtons("policy", "Политика:", choices = list("Экспансионная" = "expansion", "Сбалансированная" = "balanced", "Сдержанная" = "conservative"), selected = "balanced"), plotlyOutput("scatterPlot", height = paste0(input$client_height * 0.5, "px")) ) ) } }) output$scatterPlot <- renderPlotly({ req(input$region, input$policy) region_selected <- input$region policy_selected <- input$policy weights <- switch(policy_selected, "expansion" = c(dd = 0.45, cog = 0.35, PCI = 0.20), "balanced" = c(dd = 0.50, cog = 0.35, PCI = 0.15), "conservative" = c(dd = 0.60, cog = 0.25, PCI = 0.15)) region_eci <- ECI[1, region_selected] plot_data <- data.frame( product_code = rownames(dd), dd_value = dd[[region_selected]], cog_value = cog[[region_selected]], PCI = PCI$PCI ) %>% filter(!is.na(dd_value) & !is.na(cog_value) & cog_value != 0 & PCI >= region_eci) if (nrow(plot_data) == 0) return(NULL) plot_data$import_value <- imp$total_import_value[match(plot_data$product_code, rownames(imp))] plot_data$import_value[is.na(plot_data$import_value)] <- 0 plot_data$import_value <- plot_data$import_value / 1000 plot_data <- plot_data %>% left_join(select(product_mapping, commodity_code, commodity_fullname_english, section_code, section_name, section_color), by = c("product_code" = "commodity_code")) %>% filter(!is.na(commodity_fullname_english) & !is.na(section_name)) plot_data$commodity_fullname_english <- trimws(plot_data$commodity_fullname_english) plot_data$section_name <- trimws(plot_data$section_name) plot_data$short_product_name <- shorten_text(plot_data$commodity_fullname_english) plot_data$short_section_name <- shorten_text(plot_data$section_name) plot_data <- plot_data %>% mutate( PCI_norm = normalize_minmax(PCI), cog_norm = normalize_minmax(cog_value), dd_norm = (max(dd_value, na.rm = TRUE) - dd_value) / (max(dd_value, na.rm = TRUE) - min(dd_value, na.rm = TRUE)), composite_index = weights["dd"] * dd_norm + weights["cog"] * cog_norm + weights["PCI"] * PCI_norm ) top_50_products <- plot_data %>% arrange(desc(composite_index)) %>% slice_head(n = 50) %>% pull(product_code) plot_data <- plot_data %>% mutate( highlight = ifelse(product_code %in% top_50_products, 1, 0), alpha_value = ifelse(highlight == 1, 1, 0.2) ) plot_data$tooltip_text <- sprintf( "Продукт: %s
PCI (продуктовая сложность): %.3f
Объем торговли: %s млн $
Секция: %s", shorten_text(plot_data$short_product_name, 40), # Ограничиваем названия plot_data$PCI, format(round(plot_data$import_value, 2), big.mark = ","), shorten_text(plot_data$short_section_name, 30) ) p <- ggplot(plot_data, aes( x = dd_value, y = cog_value, size = import_value, color = section_color, text = tooltip_text, alpha = alpha_value )) + geom_point() + scale_alpha_identity() + scale_color_identity(guide = "none") + theme_minimal() + labs( title = "", subtitle = "", x = "Дистанция", y = "Прирост сложности", size = "Импорт (млн. $)" ) + theme( plot.title = element_text(size = 14, face = "bold"), legend.position = "none", axis.title = element_text(size = 10), axis.text = element_text(size = 8) ) ggplotly(p, tooltip = "text") }) } # Запуск приложения shinyApp(ui = ui, server = server)
